{"tid":486064,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"努力做人係為乜？","createTime":"2017-12-01T13:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T15:20:16.000Z","uid":766,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"152d59a92c8e3f13a61ab9839fb2d79b403c9ac9","tid":486064,"uid":766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:24:02.000Z","msg":"人類係成個宇宙係好秒小，人生幾十年係成個世界歷史亦好短，其實人就同一粒細菌冇分別，就算你好努力做人，好叻喇做到美國總統，咁又點，都只係一粒好叻既細菌，之後就會死，就冇嚕。<br />\n咁我生存其實係為乜？為左開心？如果秒小既我而家死左，其實對成個世界冇影響，只係一粒細菌由原本既10日壽命變左5日。<br />\n其實大家知唔知自己生存係為乜，你每日好努力去令自己人生進步，搵錢，充實自己，其實係為乜？<br />\n定其實由細俾人洗腦要咁做？會唔會好似ocamp 既game一生人一次咁，個答案就係死，你一死就會結束呢個遊戲，跳出呢個世界，另一個世界先係真正既世界？<br />\n<br />\n利申：9up, 下星期繼續返工努力做人"},{"pid":"6ebf77640ad33355591f8a522c2b8495929dd926","tid":486064,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"我哋身處嘅世界係一個模擬器嚟,就好似玩sims咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7da046c6e8c3d840dedb1cefa839b51c55a6f6","tid":486064,"uid":766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我哋身處嘅世界係一個模擬器嚟,就好似玩sims咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁而家姐係點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做緊乜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdd64dfbb32c462641877364da5209b05b40e45","tid":486064,"uid":766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以答我呀"},{"pid":"4e310d21532b0c215117a789a44dec4dde5b15c9","tid":486064,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我哋身處嘅世界係一個模擬器嚟,就好似玩sims咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁而家姐係點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做緊乜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有嘢都係數據嚟,所有感覺都係假嘅"},{"pid":"3980a81a022da1caac9549f14dd447f497b666e1","tid":486064,"uid":766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce687347fe7c8f78923ddecc411dfc7f39b690a","tid":486064,"uid":26653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"及時生樂 想做就做"},{"pid":"8eb5383c48c28fee40fc5f87d283f062b97d21b2","tid":486064,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"渺"},{"pid":"6f4ba4812b5437ea4d9670a7133b67ed8d942ab7","tid":486064,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:18:36.000Z","msg":"唔努力會俾人話廢"},{"pid":"5a48340b6e4b3fc1301c45693671d230d5a786a5","tid":486064,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔努力會俾人話廢</blockquote><br />\n你變咗為別人而活，成為奴隸？"},{"pid":"78dd1a2dd251c971c03c51b585d644fb1de074bf","tid":486064,"uid":766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T20:16:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔努力會俾人話廢</blockquote><br />\n你變咗為別人而活，成為奴隸？</blockquote><br />\n現實就係咁"},{"pid":"a873039dd39c1f4d2eae16357cd31da935ed2433","tid":486064,"uid":766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8270344cdf226d100463685cf2ef3bc11083d9da","tid":486064,"uid":159848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔努力會俾人話廢</blockquote><br />\n你變咗為別人而活，成為奴隸？</blockquote><br />\n除非你一個人就可以生存係呢個世界 否則認命吧"}]}